channel.title: 317 deob connect
channel.description: Well some people told me to use the 317 deob for my first client since it has been untouched, but when I try to logon to a server it says unexpected response from server please try a different world. I can log onto the same server with a different client so it's not the server it has to be the 317 deob. How do I fix this?
